proteomicsdb.org.requesttool.model.request

Enum RequestEvent

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<RequestEvent>
      • proteomicsdb.org.requesttool.model.request.RequestEvent
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<RequestEvent>

    public enum RequestEvent
extends java.lang.Enum<RequestEvent>
    An enum, that contains all possible values of the state of the RequestHandler. It has values for the standard workflow and several error values. Each value is assigned a number to indicate the estimated progress of the RequestHandler; errors have the value -1.
